  "rationale": "<p>Apply the exponent quotient rule: m<sup>20</sup>/m<sup>8</sup> = m<sup>12</sup>, and n<sup>4</sup>/n<sup>15</sup> = n<sup>\u221211</sup> = 1/n<sup>11</sup>. So the expression equals m<sup>12</sup>/n<sup>11</sup>. Choice (d) is correct.</p>",
